articles.title: Europe’s Mars orbiter to read the signals in ‘blind’ dates with China’s rover - South China Morning Post
articles.description: Chinese probe Zhu Rong will use European orbiter to send data to Earth in communication tests – ‘blind’ because the two spacecraft use incompatible frequencies.

articles.author: David M. Herszenhorn
articles.title: At G20 summit, ‘Survivor’ becomes literal for world leaders - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: The dual calamities of COVID-19 and climate change will dominate the agenda, with many worried world leaders are falling short on both.
